Indices.Message:
For a period of time, when an attack is blocked,
a shockwave will be emitted.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the
effect.
LV.6: Increases damage.</COL>

Channel a light from your rod towards the enemy.
Slowly accumulates the Torpor debilitation over
time.
With more than 1 Force Gauge, the effect will
increase.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases the rate of Torpor
accumulation.
LV.6: Increases the range of the effect.</COL>

Channel a light from your rod towards the enemy.
Slowly accumulates the Sleep debilitation over
time.
With more than 1 Force Gauge, the effect will
increase.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases the rate of Sleep
accumulation.
LV.6: Increases the range of the effect.</COL>

Rush forward with your greatshield, blowing away
enemies.
With more than 1 Force Gauge, the effect will
increase.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases damage.
LV.6: Increases moving distance and number of
hits.</COL>

Decreases attribute damage taken and debilitation
build-up
for nearby allies (determined by element granted
to rod).
With more than 1 Force Gauge, the duration will
increase.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration and power
of the effect.
LV.6: Increases the range of the effect.</COL>

Shake the earth, staggering enemies in a
wide range. Staggers large enemies and
some formidable foes.
フォースゲージ１本以上の時、消費して詠唱時間短縮
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Shortens casting time.
LV.6: Increases the range of the effect.</COL>

Use magick to create an anchor, binding the enemy.
Inflicts ATK Down, MATK Down, and slowly builds
DEF Down, MDEF Down to large and some formidable
enemies.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Decrease Stamina cost.
Increase Debilitation rate.
LV.6: Increases the range of the effect.</COL>

Create walls of magick that increase the range
of your shield's ability to block.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the
effect.
LV.6: Makes the effect protect all of your
sides.</COL>

Channel a light from your rod towards the enemy.
Slowly accumulates a debilitation that decreases
attribute
defense of enemies (determined by element granted
to rod).
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases the rate of
debilitation accumulation.
LV.6: Increases the range of the effect.</COL>

Deflect enemy attacks with your greatshield,
stunning them.
The impact will accumulate debilitations on
enemies.
With more than 1 Force Gauge, the effect will
increase.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases damage.
LV.6: Increases the duration of the counter
stance.</COL>

Guard an area around you,
nullifying damage for all allies nearby.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Shortens casting time.
LV.6: Increases the size of the effect.</COL>

Fire a magickal anchor towards a foe, and
gradually
fill the force gauge and aggression meter if it
hits.
While the anchor is active, you can move in any
direction
with <PADM>the left stick.<KEYM>the movement
keys.</KEYM>
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Decreases stamina consumption
for each additional
hit while the anchor is active.
LV.6: Increases range of the skill.</COL>

Keep the rod focused on an enemy, and radiate a
light that
builds up the Petrified status abnormality on
them.
When the Force Gauge has one or more charges,
they will be
automatically consumed to increase the skill's
performance.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases Petrified status
accumulation.
LV.6: Increases the range of the light.</COL>

Shake the Greatshield about while running around
enemies,
preventing their attacks and increasing
aggression.
When the Force Gauge has one or more charges,
they will be
automatically consumed to increase the skill's
performance.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases damage of the skill.
LV.6: Increases Guard Power and number of
hits.</COL>

EX Additional Effects:
Blow off the rocks from earth and deal damage to
enemies.
Increase damage agaisnt War-ready enemies.

EX Additional Effects:
Attract enemies within the area.
Cause status abnormality of the currently
enchanted element
of your weapon.

EX Additional Effects:
Increase casting speed.
Increase damage.
Possible to block guard-break attacks.

EX Additional Effects:
Increase Force Gauge gained by blocking.
Restore stamina when blocking attacks
and attracting enemies.

EX Additional Effects:
Increase damage and knockout power.
Further increase damage and number of hits
when a Force Gauge is consumed.
<COL ff7878> Further increase damage against
Construct/Demon/War-Ready type enemies.</COL>

EX Additional Effects:
Guard yourself during execution.
After blocking an enemy's attack,
Force Gauge increases with every hit.

EX Additional Effects:
Reduce charge time.
Can release magick wall and attack surrounding
enemies.
Blocking attacks will accumulate the energy of
the wall,
increasing damage.

EX Additional Effects:
Increase Physical/Magick defense and Endurance.
